citations.narrative:
A responsible adult facility representative was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process
at 5:15-5:45pm on 7/6/2023. I called the number on file and an adult at the address said the licensee has moved and no
longer operates their business here.
If this license is no longer being used, please send an update to our office in writing with the status of this licensed site.
End Section
